title: BucketEntryType
description:
BucketEntryType is an XDR Enum defined as:

```text enum BucketEntryType { METAENTRY = -1, // At-and-after protocol 11: bucket metadata, should come first. LIVEENTRY = 0, // Before protocol 11: created-or-updated; // At-and-after protocol 11: only updated. DEADENTRY = 1, INITENTRY = 2 // At-and-after protocol 11: only created. }; ```
